metadata.name: Essence
metadata.description:
Essence is about unlocking a negative mindset. 

Fear and negativity can manifest in your mind, preventing clarity, growth and general happiness. If left unchecked it can grow and worsen with time. Understanding that all perceptions of a problem or circumstances happen only in your mind and that you have the ability to change it. You don’t necessarily need to change the thing that is causing you negative impact; it can be resolved by just changing the way you see and feel about what’s happening around you.

Free yourself before fear or negativity takes root.
